Module mm
Package mm.utilities.ObjectsConf

Class BallConf

  • java.lang.Object
    • mm.utilities.ObjectsConf.ObjectConf
      • mm.utilities.ObjectsConf.BallConf
  • public class BallConf
extends ObjectConf
    Configuration class representing a ball object in the physics simulation. Extends the generic ObjectConf with radius, density, and friction properties.

        Constructs a BallConf with position and radius. Angle is set to 0, density and friction to -1 (static).
        Parameters:
        x - X position of the ball center (meters).
        y - Y position of the ball center (meters).
        radius - Radius of the ball (meters).
